    "Good, that's what I like to see." He said in referance to Hot Rod's not 
trusting him. "Okay, about the Matrix. How powerful is it exactly? Is it just 
as powerful as the Autobot one? Because I have reason to belive that Unicron 
is going to return, and that the Judge will control all of Cybertron."
